tiers.ability_description: At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.

If all allies are First Order at the start of battle, First Order allies gain Damage Immunity for 2 turns. Whenever a First Order ally is critically hit, all First Order allies gain 10% Critical Damage (stacking, max 50%) until the end of the encounter. Whenever a First Order ally attacks out of turn, all First Order allies gain 10% Offense (stacking, max 50%) until the end of the encounter.
The first time First Order Stormtrooper is defeated, they are revived with 100% Health, gain Protection Over Time (75%) for 2 turns, and take a bonus turn.
At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.

If all allies are Pirates at the start of encounter, Pirate allies gain 3 stacks of Profit. Whenever Pirate allies have 15 or more combined stacks of Profit:

- Pirate Attacker allies gain Stealth for 1 turn whenever they are critically hit.
- Whenever a Pirate Tank ally uses an ability, all other Pirate allies are called to assist.
- Whenever a Pirate Support or Healer ally is inflicted with a debuff, all Pirate allies recover 5% Health and 5% Protection.

Whenever a Pirate ally consumes a stack of Profit, all Pirate allies gain 5% Defense, Max Health, Max Protection, and Offense (stacking, max 150%) for the rest of the encounter.
Whenever Hondo Ohnaka uses a Basic ability, he gains 9 additional stacks of Ransom, Protection Up (100%, stacking) for 2 turns, and reduces his cooldowns by 1.
At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.
Whenever Pirate allies inflict a debuff on an enemy during their turn, they deal bonus damage equal to 10% of that enemy's Max Health, which can't be evaded.
Whenever Light Side allies use a Special ability, they gain Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, and Health Up  for 2 turns.

Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User critically hits an enemy, dispel all debuffs on themself and gain 5% Turn Meter. Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User uses a Special ability against an enemy with at least 3 debuffs, reduce that enemy's Max Health by 5%. Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User uses a Special ability when they have at least 3 buffs that can be dispelled, gain 5% Max Health.
The first time each turn Rey gains Ultimate Charge, they gain an additional 6% Ultimate Charge.
At the start of the encounter, the weakest ally gains 20% Turn Meter for every Light Side ally.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Critical Chance Up, Critical Damage Up, and Offense Up for 2 turns.

At the start of the encounter, the weakest ally gains 20% Turn Meter for every Light Side ally.
At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Critical Chance Up, Critical Damage Up, and Offense Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Speed Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Attacker allies use a Special Ability on their turn, they gain Riposte for 2 turns.

Each time Poggle the Lesser inflicts Ability Block, he also inflicts Burning for 2 turns on the target enemy, Poggle the Lesser gains 10% Turn Meter, and all allies gain 20% Offense (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever IG-86 critically hits an enemy, IG-86 gains Damage Immunity for 1 turn, 25% Turn Meter, and inflicts Deathmark on the target enemy for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled, evaded, or resisted. If the enemy was already Deathmarked, IG-86 gains Protection Up (50%, stacking), Retribution, and Speed Up for 2 turns.

Whenever a debuff on an enemy expires, Attacker allies gain 2% Offense, doubled if that debuff was dispelled, until the end of battle.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Speed Up for 2 turns.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.

The first time a Tank ally is defeated, revive them with 100% Health and Protection, and they gain a bonus turn. Limit once per battle.

Tank allies Taunt for 1 turn, whenever another ally is inflicted with a debuff. Whenever Tank allies Taunt, they gain Defense Up for 1 turn and 5% Crit Avoidance (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever a Tank is critically hit while Taunting, they recover 15% Health and Protection. Whenever a non-tank ally uses a Special ability, Tank allies assist, if the enemy was Taunting, deal 250% bonus damage.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
Light Side allies start the battle with +25% Turn Meter.

At the start of each turn, if non-Galactic Legend Tank allies have 50% or more Turn Meter, damage they receive is reduced by 75% until the end of the turn.
